Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.65,0:00:02.61,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,My name’s Liko.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m taking a Terastal Course \N with Roy and Dot.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We all passed our basics tests!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.45,0:00:15.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Next, we’ll be trying to finish our \N wild Pokémon reports while going camping!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.22,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There’s so many wild Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.35,0:00:35.47,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The forest over there and that river \N probably have even more.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I think I’ll be able to \N write a nice report!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.86,0:00:46.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mr. Zinnia said we should take \N photos and videos, right?{Tagged just in case: Zinnia-sensei}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.48,0:00:47.36,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.70,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,How about we use this \N as research material?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.49,0:00:54.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Professor Actually-Doing-Research Friede’s...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Professor Doing-His-Job-For-Once Friede’s...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.58,0:01:01.92,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah. Professor Friede’s \N Pokémon distribution map.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.92,0:01:05.96,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s been presented at a conference, \N and has proper sources...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.34,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,If we can find any Pokémon \N that aren’t on this map,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.43,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,our reports should turn out \N {\i1}really{\i0} glitzy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Plus, then we can \N tell the whole ship about them!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.89,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wanna get some \N Pokémon Battles in, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.89,0:01:19.52,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Good idea! \N Why not do your report on them?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.52,0:01:20.94,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess our campsite \N for the night will be...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.57,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right here!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.96,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,All right! My tent’s all good!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?! Already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.05,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I’m used to this kinda stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:16.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.31,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Goodness, now I’ll have to \N start all over.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.04,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Won’t that rock get in your way?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.46,0:03:51.46,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Nope, it’ll make for a perfect workstation.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.00,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.88,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Maybe I should also—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.80,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.22,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What is it, Nyarote?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.85,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen that Pokémon before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.98,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Kunugidama. Bagworm Pokémon. \N Bug type.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.94,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It likes to make its shell thicker \N by adding layers of tree bark.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.82,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,The extra weight is not a burden.{Scarlet dex entry, partially edited}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.61,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hey, what’s that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ve almost got you all nice and clean.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’ll be your turn next, Nyarote.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I looked it up earlier,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.86,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,and apparently Kunugidama \N can explode when they’re surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.15,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that{\i0} was that boom I heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.78,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Was that a splash?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.54,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.05,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You mind if we go after it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.72,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wanna write my report \N on that Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.72,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.76,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.77,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Sure! Let’s go, Hogator! Kaiden!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We better not fall behind, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.61,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Let’s head back to the tent \N and research the local Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We’ll stay here a while longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.32,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos can roam free here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t wander too far, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Nyarote.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ll wipe you off.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry Nyarote, just a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You got yourself dirty again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos! \N I told you not to go too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What was it, Nyarote?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.68,0:06:52.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote’s fur is all prickly, \N like spines...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.74,0:07:16.17,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,If I’m writing a report, \N I want it to be on a really impressive Pokémon...{impact line}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.04,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Are there any good candidates \N around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.30,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ooh, this looks interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.39,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.65,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.24,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Liko... Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.91,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Have a fight with Nyarote?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,N-Not a fight, really...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.54,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s just... She’s in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.50,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.26,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Decided on a report topic yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.59,0:08:08.55,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Then let’s share info. \N Check this out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.05,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Apparently, something called a “flower pillar” \N can happen near here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.56,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A flower pillar?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.56,0:08:17.56,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It says a huge amount of flower petals \N are whipped up into the air,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.56,0:08:21.56,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,making a pillar of flowers \N linking together the land and sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But as for what causes it, \N or when it’ll happen next...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.49,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Or what plant the petals come from...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.57,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s a mysterious phenomenon \N with a lot of unknowns.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.25,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Plus, there’s a rumor floating around \N about this flower pillar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A rumor?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.50,0:08:43.17,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s said that anyone who sees the flower pillar \N is sure to find happiness.{happy line}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.76,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Well, it’s a story with \N a lot of fuzzy details.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.76,0:08:58.52,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But it sounds really impressive and glitzy, \N and a local Pokémon might be behind it all,{impact line}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.02,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,so I think I’m gonna go \N look for it later.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.31,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I-I want to look, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,If I can see it with Nyarote...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.74,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.82,0:09:16.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote... Um, I just heard about \N something wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.33,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot told me about this \N “flower pillar” thing that happens nearby—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Uh... Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos is gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It wandered off alone again?!{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.30,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.09,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nyarote! I’ll tell you later!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s get Terapagos first, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.70,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Okay, we should get going too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.45,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh? Will that take long?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.12,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ack! Don’t tell me...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.92,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,H-H-H-H-H-H-H-H-H-H-H-Hold it!{compared against the waveform and yeah I think this is the right amount of stutters. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.17,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.88,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,If you break this, our dinner plans \N are down the drain, you hear me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.60,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Kanuchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I was sure it went this way...{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hey, Nyarote, help me look.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.42,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What is it, Mibrim?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You want to play?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Not here, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Are those...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, look after Mibrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah, these are \N Terapagos’s footprints...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It came through here.{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.13,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There’s more over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.80,0:12:20.89,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}These{\i0} don’t seem like \N Terapagos prints, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.33,0:12:48.08,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Was that noise a Kunugidama?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.84,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote... Mibrim...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.85,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote! Mibrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.35,0:13:11.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Nyarote...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote! Mibrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Did I get...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,...separated from them?
Comment: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.66,0:14:55.42,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What do I do? I can’t climb out...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.42,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Not to mention... it’s so hot...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Pokémon...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.19,0:15:20.86,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Nonokurage. Wood Ear Pokémon. \N Ground/Grass type.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.11,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It lives in muggy forests.{Partial Scarlet dex entry}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.99,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Its legs may be thin, but when it gets going, \N it can run at a speed of fifty kilometers per hour.{Partial Violet dex entry, partially edited}{intentional scenebleed}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nonokurage?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There’s so many vines...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.89,0:15:49.72,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait, are they...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos and Mibrim, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote is trying to protect me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.63,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.13,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.76,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t attack them.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You’re trying to protect me, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.85,0:16:41.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They haven’t done anything to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nyarote.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.84,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You just need those vines gone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.46,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Are they waiting for something?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The wind’s blowing through \N where the vines just were!{TL: The wind’s blowing through where the vines were!}{note that the edit is barely different from the TL, only adding the word "just"... which pushes the line from 15cps to 17cps. I also thought of "The wind's blowing through where the vines used to be!" which is... also exactly 17cps. I couldn't think of a take I liked that was less than 17cps. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.91,0:19:40.12,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Is this... the flower pillar?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.13,0:19:57.68,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You know, I heard that anyone who sees \N this flower pillar linking the land and sky...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.89,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,...will be able to find happiness.{happy line}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.93,0:20:06.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m glad everyone’s here to see this... \N Especially you, Nyarote.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So soft...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.55,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,You saw the flower pillar?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.92,0:20:37.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The flower petals turned out to be \N Nonokurage flaps.{ENgame: Toedscool Flaps}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.59,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Sounds like that’ll make \N an awesome report!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.39,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.02,0:20:50.65,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,So the strong wind blowing over \N the hot ground caused a tornado...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.65,0:20:58.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,And the Nonokurage around here are in the habit \N of using that wind to get their flaps to peel off...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.66,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,By the way... \N You got it on video, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh? H-How about photos...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.58,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry... I forgot...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.16,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wh-What a waste...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I think I’ll draw \N an illustration for my report.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.09,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I got a good look at it, \N so it’s clear in my mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.38,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Lemme see it when you’re done!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.55,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.05,0:21:24.30,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Learning about a new Pokémon \N through the flower pillar was nice and all,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,but getting to learn \N a bit more about Nyarote...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I can certainly say I’m happy.{happy line}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,How about you, Nyarote?
Comment: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.16,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.16,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time for my Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.79,0:21:54.50,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today, let’s take a look at \N the Wood Ear Pokémon, Nonokurage.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.13,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It looks like Menokurage, \N but it’s a different Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.13,0:22:01.01,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s said to excel at something,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.80,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but do you know what that thing is?{options: all are words ending in -ashi, so tried to keep a foot connection with run/leap/step but eh}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.80,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.48,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.40,0:23:44.49,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,The answer is A: Running away!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.49,0:23:48.28,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,It’s cowardly, and will run away \N immediately if enemies draw near.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.49,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,It’s said to be able to flee \N at fifty kilometers per hour!
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.50,0:24:02.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.50,0:24:06.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What is the Habanero Pokémon \N of the Paldea Region?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.55,0:24:08.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.22,0:24:09.84,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Capsaiji!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.84,0:24:11.01,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Amazing, Dot!{Sasuga. line}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.10,0:24:19.48,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{\q2}Apparently, the front teeth that Capsaiji shed \N are even used in traditional super-spicy Paldean cuisine!{Violet dex entry}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.40,0:24:24.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so! To be continued next time \N on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.53,0:24:26.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Kaiden, Strong Wind Warning!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.95,0:24:28.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s got nothing to do with Capsaiji?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
