Dialogue: 11,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.36,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=1047}{\blur0.6\fad(350,0)\1a&HFF&\t(305,350,\1a&H00&)}Together, we challenge, chasing the future
Dialogue: 11,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.37,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.04,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We gather, let’s catch it, chasing tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Hey, let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.50,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Never give up - Every time you fall, stand up
Dialogue: 11,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.13,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:45.13,0:01:45.92,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.17,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Imagining, dreaming, with my friend (oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.97,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The light ahead of us, so bright
Dialogue: 11,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.09,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Once it catches your eye
Dialogue: 11,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.26,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The rest is easy, leave it to me
Dialogue: 11,0:01:57.26,0:02:01.10,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You and I will add to our story (oh-oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.06,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Always a little bit more (We are)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Closer than yesterday (Best friends)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.40,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}I’m making my debut into a new world with you
Dialogue: 11,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:12.32,0:02:16.82,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}It’s set into motion now, our fateful adventure
Dialogue: 11,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.41,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.58,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Watch us, tell us...
Dialogue: 11,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.96,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy, let’s go)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:23.96,0:02:28.42,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We are buddy-buddy-buddies, chasing piles of dreams
Dialogue: 11,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.51,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Wish it, and it’ll come true, you know it
Dialogue: 11,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.84,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Get over here, Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:02:31.84,0:02:35.80,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Now, to chase spark-spark-sparkling bright tomorrows
Dialogue: 11,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.76,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Leap out into that vast sky
Dialogue: 11,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You sparkling Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.39,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:43.39,0:02:48.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Hand in hand, flying up-up-up higher
Dialogue: 11,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.70,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.24,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.03,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Let’s challenge
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.36,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(350,0)\1a&HFF&\t(305,350,\1a&H00&)}Together, we challenge, chasing the future
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.37,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Let’s go!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.04,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We gather, let’s catch it, chasing tomorrow
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Hey, let’s go!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.50,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Never give up - Every time you fall, stand up
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.13,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.13,0:01:45.92,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(hey buddy)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.17,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Imagining, dreaming, with my friend (oh)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.97,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}The light ahead of us, so bright
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.09,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Once it catches your eye
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.26,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}The rest is easy, leave it to me
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.26,0:02:01.10,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}You and I will add to our story (oh-oh)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.06,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Always a little bit more (We are)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Closer than yesterday (Best friends)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.40,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}I’m making my debut into a new world with you
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.32,0:02:16.82,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}It’s set into motion now, our fateful adventure
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.41,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.58,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Watch us, tell us...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.96,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(hey buddy, let’s go)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.96,0:02:28.42,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We are buddy-buddy-buddies, chasing piles of dreams
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.51,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Wish it, and it’ll come true, you know it
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.84,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Get over here, Challenger
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.84,0:02:35.80,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Now, to chase spark-spark-sparkling bright tomorrows
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.76,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Leap out into that vast sky
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}You sparkling Challenger
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.39,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.39,0:02:48.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hand in hand, flying up-up-up higher
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.70,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.24,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.03,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=1048}{\blur8\shad0\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Let’s challenge
